Have my doctors
confirm that the Queen
is still fertile.

68
00:07:12,581 --> 00:07:13,891
The people need
to be reassured.

69
00:07:13,958 --> 00:07:14,939
I care
for your safety.

70
00:07:15,014 --> 00:07:17,216
The threats to your
person are real.

71
