Majesty.

79
00:08:29,571 --> 00:08:32,701
Send me back to England
to begin God's work.

80
00:08:53,793 --> 00:08:55,201
Your Majesty.

81
00:09:12,898 --> 00:09:15,003
Guards!
Take hold of him!

82
00:09:17,376 --> 00:09:19,744
