Majesty.

84
00:09:26,753 --> 00:09:28,475
A puddle.

85
00:09:50,783 --> 00:09:51,928
Puddle.

86
00:09:58,687 --> 00:10:00,596
You'll have to see
the Lord Chamberlain, sir.

87
00:10:00,672 --> 00:10:01,849
Which one is he?

88
00:10:01,918 --> 00:10:03,643
He's over there.

89
00:10:03,743 --> 00:10:05,336
You can't come in.

90
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:07,807
