to come out.

92
00:10:09,918 --> 00:10:10,868
And when will he
come out?

93
00:10:10,943 --> 00:10:12,056
There's no way
of knowing that.

94
00:10:12,126 --> 00:10:15,542
I had less trouble
than this boarding
a Spanish ship.

95
00:10:17,567 --> 00:10:21,495
