should sail up the Thames,
can the docks be closed?

96
00:10:21,567 --> 00:10:23,605
Not closed, Majesty.
But the gun positions...

97
00:10:23,678 --> 00:10:25,304
Spanish...

98
00:10:29,822 --> 00:10:31,416
Ambassador.

99
00:10:33,534 --> 00:10:35,389
King Eric of Sweden,
Majesty.

100
00:10:35,455 --> 00:10:36,698
Not again.

101
00:10:36,767 --> 00:10:37,813
Still madly in love with you.

102
00:10:37,885 --> 00:10:38,932
Still mad, you mean.

103
00:10:39,005 --> 00:10:41,941
Lvan, Tsar
of all the Russias.

104
00:10:42,014 --> 00:10:43,421
Where's Bess?

105
00:10:43,518 --> 00:10:46,452
Known as
"lvan the Terrible," Majesty.

106
00:10:53,309 --> 00:10:54,455
Late.

107
00:10:54,525 --> 00:10:56,730
I beg
Your Majesty's forgiveness.

108
00:10:57,053 --> 00:10:58,841
Given.

109
00:11:01,822 --> 00:11:03,610
Once.

110
00:11:03,677 --> 00:11:06,677
The Archduke
Charles of Austria, Majesty.

111
00:11:10,557 --> 00:11:13,013
The puddle man
is outside, Majesty.

112
00:11:13,085 --> 00:11:14,164
My suitors.

113
00:11:14,236 --> 00:11:17,620
Younger brother
to Maximilian II,
Holy Roman Emperor.

114
00:11:17,693 --> 00:11:20,115
Cousin of Philip of Spain.
Wealthy.

115
00:11:20,188 --> 00:11:22,708
He's rather handsome.

116
00:11:25,052 --> 00:11:26,034
How old is he?

117
00:11:26,109 --> 00:11:28,475
Young,
I believe, Majesty.

118
00:11:29,884 --> 00:11:32,087
An Austrian alliance
would keep France quiet.

119
00:11:32,155 --> 00:11:34,360
And put Philip on a leash.

120
00:11:34,427 --> 00:11:36,283
I've become
almost enthusiastic.

121
00:11:37,948 --> 00:11:40,120
Send for him.

122
