123
00:11:42,620 --> 00:11:45,969
How much longer
do you think I can play
this game, Francis?

124
00:11:46,043 --> 00:11:48,946
Virginity is an asset
that holds its value well.

125
00:11:49,019 --> 00:11:50,874
Walter Raleigh, Majesty.

126
00:11:52,731 --> 00:11:55,731
Your Majesty, this man
is a notorious pirate.

127
00:11:55,803 --> 00:12:00,472
Spanish gold stolen
from Spanish ships,
attacked without provocation.

128
00:12:04,155 --> 00:12:07,602
Well, sir, what do you want?

129
00:12:07,674 --> 00:12:10,707
I have just returned
from the New World, Majesty.

130
00:12:10,778 --> 00:12:13,299
I have claimed
the fertile coast
in your name

131
00:12:13,371 --> 00:12:15,990
and called it Virginia

132
00:12:16,058 --> 00:12:18,393
in honor
of our Virgin Queen.

133
00:12:18,458 --> 00:12:20,215
Virginia?

134
