And when I marry,
will you change
the name to Conjugia?

135
00:12:25,145 --> 00:12:26,902
I ask your gracious
permission, Majesty,

136
00:12:26,970 --> 00:12:29,556
to return to the New World
with your royal warrant

137
00:12:29,626 --> 00:12:32,474
to found a colony
under the laws
and protections of England.

138
00:12:32,538 --> 00:12:33,749
He wants money.

139
00:12:33,818 --> 00:12:35,990
Who are they?

140
00:12:36,057 --> 00:12:38,360
Natives of the
Americas, Majesty.

141
00:12:42,010 --> 00:12:43,635
Have they no ruler
of their own?

142
00:12:43,706 --> 00:12:46,389
None to match
England's Queen.

143
00:12:46,457 --> 00:12:47,886
These gentlemen
are welcome.

144
00:12:47,961 --> 00:12:49,717
See that they
are treated well.

145
00:12:49,786 --> 00:12:51,696
I also come
bearing gifts
for Your Majesty.

146
00:12:51,769 --> 00:12:56,144
These gifts, Majesty,
are the fruits of piracy,

147
00:12:56,216 --> 00:12:58,388
the true property
of the realm of Spain.

148
00:12:58,457 --> 00:13:01,873
Let's see, shall we?
What have you brought me?

149
00:13:10,105 --> 00:13:12,855
<i>Patata, Majesty.</i>

150
00:13:12,921 --> 00:13:15,855
You eat it.
Very nourishing.

151
00:13:35,192 --> 00:13:36,719
Tobacco.

152
00:13:38,456 --> 00:13:40,876
You breathe its smoke.

153
00:13:40,951 --> 00:13:43,951
Very stimulating.

154
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,542
Gold.

155
00:13:56,246 --> 00:13:59,727
Courtesy of a Spanish ship
that found itself unable
to complete its journey.

156
00:13:59,799 --> 00:14:01,774
Forgive me, Majesty.

157
00:14:01,847 --> 00:14:05,426
I find the air
has become stale.

158
00:14:05,495 --> 00:14:08,878
I am sensitive
to the smell
of open sewers.

159
00:14:15,318 --> 00:14:19,542
I cannot accept
the fruits of piracy,
Mr. Raleigh.

160
00:14:19,606 --> 00:14:23,250
Philip of Spain is no friend
of England, Majesty.

161
00:14:23,318 --> 00:14:27,509
The more gold I take from him,
the safer you will be.

162
00:14:27,573 --> 00:14:29,995
Well, well.

163
00:14:30,071 --> 00:14:31,924
A political pirate.

164
00:14:31,990 --> 00:14:35,732
